WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:01.931
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.931 --> 00:00:04.194
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.194 --> 00:00:05.428
Praise the Lord.

00:00:05.428 --> 00:00:07.089
Well, I've seen a lot today.

00:00:07.839 --> 00:00:12.800
Just like I always do, I take communion and I drive around and pray in the spirit.

00:00:14.319 --> 00:00:25.980
I passed the fire station on my right, and as I passed it, I heard '911, 911.

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:36.754
' I saw the emergency responders responding to an emergency: major turbulence ahead.

00:00:37.131 --> 00:00:41.653
I looked at the fire station and I thought, 'Lord, what's going on?

00:00:41.653 --> 00:00:48.113
' All of a sudden, I went into deep groaning and travail in the spirit, praying in the spirit.

00:00:48.970 --> 00:00:53.689
The Lord started to speak to me very strongly.

00:00:53.689 --> 00:01:06.760
He started showing me a Pearl Harbor event as we see in the days ahead.

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:17.794
China is becoming desperate, and North Korea is becoming desperate, wanting out from underneath the Western boot.

00:01:20.420 --> 00:01:32.080
I saw North Korea—because they are the social pariah—becoming the person rising up to become the bully.

00:01:35.868 --> 00:01:37.720
Does that make sense?

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:48.799
It's like the head mafia guy who has his little thugs underneath him that do the bidding for the head mafia leader.

00:01:49.820 --> 00:01:55.086
Like the Godfather, and then the Godfather has henchmen.

00:01:55.086 --> 00:01:58.320
He has the guys underneath him that carry out the bad things.

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:06.150
China was the Godfather, and North Korea was the hitman.

00:02:06.440 --> 00:02:12.400
That's what I was seeing; it's the only way I can describe what I saw.

00:02:12.816 --> 00:02:25.280
I saw North Korea being the pawn because of the political side of China having its fingers in all the different countries.

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:31.080
They didn't want to be looked at as the bad guy for what's about to take place.

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:36.567
But I kept hearing when I was praying, 'Remember Pearl Harbor.

00:02:36.567 --> 00:02:37.013
Remember Pearl Harbor.

00:02:37.013 --> 00:02:41.805
' I said, 'Lord, I know that Japan was with Pearl Harbor and all that.

00:02:41.805 --> 00:02:47.280
' And He said, 'This will be a type and shadow in the days ahead.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:50.640
Remember this.

00:02:50.640 --> 00:03:03.232
' As I was interceding, the Lord was showing me even deeper into the Asian culture as a whole.

00:03:03.232 --> 00:03:07.451
They think differently than the Western culture.

00:03:07.451 --> 00:03:09.680
Do you know what I'm saying?

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:13.129
That's the only way I can describe this to you.

00:03:13.129 --> 00:03:18.507
It's kind of like how the African American culture thinks differently than the white American culture.

00:03:18.507 --> 00:03:20.000
Does that make sense?

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:35.249
Everybody thinks it's just culture, but I saw in this the Asians sticking with their culture, trying to preserve what they believe and their family ties.

00:03:36.216 --> 00:03:37.760
It's a very Asian thing.

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:47.439
I saw China being backed into a hole, and I saw a great depression, a financial infrastructure crumbling.

00:03:47.999 --> 00:03:59.113
As this happened, they didn't want to lose their 'Asianness,' their culture, or what they believed in.

00:04:01.375 --> 00:04:09.220
So they were in a place like a samurai warrior ready to turn its sword on itself.

00:04:09.220 --> 00:04:17.200
You want to die with honor; you don't want to die looking disgraceful.

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:20.000
That's the way it seemed.

00:04:22.387 --> 00:04:40.343
They were banding together as Asian cultures—North Korea trying to bring in South Korea in these demonic spirits, trying to bring in Vietnam and the Philippines, all coming together to combat the Western culture.

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:50.133
This was part of the vision that I was seeing.

00:04:50.626 --> 00:05:00.270
I kept hearing 'Pearl Harbor' echoing in the spirit, a retaliation.

00:05:01.272 --> 00:05:07.634
Then the Lord showed me Canada.

00:05:08.108 --> 00:05:13.669
I started praying for Canada, and the Lord showed me the scales.

00:05:14.526 --> 00:05:22.080
They have been weighed and found lacking because of the way the people voted.

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:27.830
Not all Canadians voted this way.

00:05:27.830 --> 00:05:35.420
Let me say this very clearly: not all Canadians voted this way, but the majority...

00:05:35.420 --> 00:05:41.507
I told you all, the Lord said, 'Pray that it's too big to rig.

00:05:41.507 --> 00:05:51.620
' But the majority were for going left, into darkness—not conservative, but for darkness.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:06:00.150
Because of this decision, there was a scale that was tipped in the spirit realm.

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:02.400
(That was real thunder as I say this.

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:05.560
) Wow, Lord, I hear you.

00:06:06.015 --> 00:06:07.834
This is so serious.

00:06:07.834 --> 00:06:29.337
I saw the balance of the scales, and because of the decisions that were made to go the ungodly way with sexual perversion, laws, and things that would be put into place, I saw: 'You want this, you can have it.

00:06:29.337 --> 00:06:42.857
' I saw a new type of STD, a new venereal disease that had never been seen before, which is very gross.

00:06:43.286 --> 00:06:50.274
This is what I saw coming through certain practices.

00:06:50.589 --> 00:06:57.199
Because I know I have children watching me, I'm trying to be careful how I say this because I have pure ears listening.

00:06:59.880 --> 00:07:03.000
Certain practices are ungodly.

00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:16.057
Because of these ungodly acts and the reprobate mind wanting to go this way, the scales in the spirit realm were weighed and found lacking.

00:07:16.503 --> 00:07:18.857
This goes for America also.

00:07:18.857 --> 00:07:38.789
I saw it up by Quebec, and it infiltrated into New York, Boston, and these major cities—a new venereal disease that has never been known before, worse than the AIDS virus.

00:07:38.789 --> 00:07:40.660
Do you understand what I'm trying to say?

00:07:40.660 --> 00:07:45.909
This is a new virus coming onto the scene.

00:07:45.919 --> 00:08:02.229
I saw judgment begin even in Japan concerning the trafficking coming up from Mexico.

00:08:02.229 --> 00:08:20.087
And I saw, because of touching the children and the young people, this venereal disease will make them eunuchs because of the infection.

00:08:20.087 --> 00:08:29.240
I saw so much infection that they have to do something because there's no cure for it.

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:41.595
It's a new type of virus, a very serious virus that is transmitted through...

00:08:44.608 --> 00:08:47.519
This is very serious.

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:55.440
I saw such a darkness, and the anger of the Lord was so strong.

00:08:55.440 --> 00:09:00.112
I thought I was going to vibrate out of my car as He spoke.

00:09:00.456 --> 00:09:05.230
The anger was like the thunder above my heavens right now.

00:09:05.230 --> 00:09:14.745
It was that loud, as I hear the rain and the hail.

00:09:14.745 --> 00:09:22.600
It was very strong—the rebuke and the warning coming from the Father.

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:29.017
He told me, 'Because of these things that you are seeing, decisions have been made.

00:09:29.017 --> 00:09:43.440
' Decisions have been made, and you will see a judgment coming on these circumstances because of sexual promiscuity.

00:09:46.330 --> 00:09:54.389
I know I probably butchered it, but I try with my English.

00:10:17.485 --> 00:10:17.942
This is what I saw.

00:10:17.942 --> 00:10:27.861
Then I saw a mega-earthquake from British Columbia all the way down to San Francisco.

00:10:41.590 --> 00:10:41.901
It was an earthquake so massive and devastating on the West Coast that it shook the foundation of the earth.

00:10:52.685 --> 00:10:57.693
